{"tid":435941,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］十月十五日月色真美川越祭","createTime":"2017-10-14T17:13:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T15:52:47.000Z","uid":8203,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"92e5469a31e02820a998d5e02668d04d475d4031","tid":435941,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T17:13:27.000Z","msg":"話說我呢D真毒睇完就好似睇完秒五咁無乜感觸可言<br />\n只可以講這些機會不是屬於我的<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都好憧憬呢段故事既<br />\n加上冰川神社D風鈴真係好吸引我 於是就決定去川越祭順便聖地巡禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n首先搭車去川越其間會翻睇一次月色真美<br />\n然後記低值得聖巡既舞台 再去影<br />\n利申先 垃圾iphone垃圾技術<br />\n<a href=\"http://astral01.hatenablog.com/entry/2017/07/11/213731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fastral01.hatenablog.com%2Fentry%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F213731&d=3kdSw36gXA8gdioUiDeTTP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=a0966f07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">astral01.hatenablog.com/entry/2017/07/11/213731</a><br />\n想睇真聖巡就睇架仔 我都係跟佢<br />\n<br />\n有咩想去既地方煩請講低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我盡我所能<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你會落雨一定要帶遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c725c11018568e16c6c1b52d2d35c8ce24b275","tid":435941,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T17:18:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/15/011743_aa65f6dc8afd5f93e3876fae66ca36bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F15%2F011743_aa65f6dc8afd5f93e3876fae66ca36bd.jpg&h=a6383fb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我好想快d瞓呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"